{"tid":829620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[RTHK]荷蘭鬼佬節目講大陸「社會信用系統」","createTime":"2018-09-20T14:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T03:54:38.000Z","uid":41818,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ef73991af4f58854e3fb06dc19ac7a59c6019598","tid":829620,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T14:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/225056_5a0b58b269313dea9b6de3ae68307bd7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F225056_5a0b58b269313dea9b6de3ae68307bd7.png&h=13474618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n科技與自由<br />\n<br />\n深圳是創新科技公司和人才的集中地。從電動車至機械人都在這裏研發和推廣。在眾多新科技當中，監控技術尤其發達。深圳街頭就設有「人臉辨識系統」，專捉衝紅燈等犯交通規例的「罪犯」，連犯五次便會被「拉黑」，購房買車等都不被允許。在創科技術的配合下，中國政府正推動社會信用系統。泰嘉儒從線眼遍佈的深圳，走到尚存一息自由空氣的澳門，看看在大數據收集下，小市民的生存之道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/throughtheheartofchina\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fthroughtheheartofchina&d=VUUc2fuwnPA%2FjAcv7wt5Zm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=1d3205cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/throughtheheartofchina</a>"},{"pid":"5ed9746a4cb913e17fef89730dd617875fd39698","tid":829620,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T19:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cc478345e8cb098130b3eaaea50f7c7a324ab1","tid":829620,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T20:06:42.000Z","msg":"個馬交女記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8185882d0e057aa7a87e38eebe6954ce1573e6","tid":829620,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T20:47:44.000Z","msg":"無信用嘅國家講信用